sp.p:
Yes, Ned—one must do summat for an honest

livelihood. Flat catching's considered fair game all the world over, you know;
       from the very top of St. James's-street, down to the bottom of St. Giles's.

By what authority ? (energetically) The authority of right over wrong—of
       virtue over villainy. By what authority ? the strongest, the most sacred—self-preservation ;
       I would not have MY NAME dishonoured!
